  "title": "Business Development/ Sales Account Manager #80447",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Technology Services</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Business Development/ Sales Account Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: Joo Chiat Road</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 9.00am - 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Commission + PB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Make outbound sales calls to assigned customers to achieve sales targets.</li><li>Act as the primary liaison among sales channels, customers, and internal teams.</li><li>Solve problems creatively to meet sales and customer objectives.</li><li>Profile and prioritize target accounts effectively.</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships across the industry.</li><li>Travel locally and overseas to meet key customers as needed.</li><li>Negotiate contract terms with clients and coordinate with stakeholders.</li><li>Derive insights from customer and competitor data.</li><li>Offer alternative brand products to replace EOL parts.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Relevant sales experience is preferred.</li><li>Open to candidates without direct sales or industry experience.</li><li>Goal oriented, determined to learn from mistakes and improve, good with people, and able to communicate convincingly.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80447 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
